{"tha-ap46:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap46:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap46:0.3":"Sannitthapakattheraapadana ","tha-ap46:1.1":"“Aranne kutikam katva, ","tha-ap46:1.2":"vasami pabbatantare; ","tha-ap46:1.3":"Labhalabhena santuttho, ","tha-ap46:1.4":"yasena ayasena ca. ","tha-ap46:2.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap46:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap46:2.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap46:2.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap46:3.1":"Upagatam mahanagam, ","tha-ap46:3.2":"jalajuttamanamakam; ","tha-ap46:3.3":"Tinasantharam pannapetva, ","tha-ap46:3.4":"adasim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap46:4.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap46:4.2":"amandam paniyancaham; ","tha-ap46:4.3":"Adasim ujubhutassa, ","tha-ap46:4.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap46:5.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap46:5.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap46:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap46:5.4":"amandassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap46:6.1":"Ekatalisakappamhi, ","tha-ap46:6.2":"eko asim arindamo; ","tha-ap46:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap46:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap46:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap46:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap46:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap46:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sannitthapako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap46:9.1":"Sannitthapakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}